---
// src/components/Hero.astro
---

<section class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center min-h-[600px]">
  
  <div class="flex flex-col items-start z-10">
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-[4rem] font-serif font-bold text-[#4A2E15] leading-none mb-6">
      Preservando a <br/> alma cearense <br/> 
      <span class="text-[#0B5D3F]">desde 1948.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-[#4A2E15]/80 mb-8 leading-relaxed max-w-md font-medium">
      A Comissão Cearense de Folclore atua na pesquisa, registro e difusão das nossas manifestações culturais, valorizando a memória e os mestres da tradição popular.
    </p>
    <a href="/sobre" class="bg-[#0B5D3F] text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-[#07422c] transition-colors font-medium text-lg shadow-lg">
      Conheça a Comissão
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="relative w-full h-[400px] md:h-[500px] flex justify-center items-center z-10">
    
    <div class="absolute w-[80%] h-[90%] bg-[#D4A373] right-4 top-0 rounded-sm"></div>

    <img 
      src="/foto-hero.jpg" 
      alt="Cultura Popular Cearense" 
      class="relative z-10 w-[90%] h-[85%] object-cover rounded-md shadow-2xl mr-8 mt-8"
    />
  </div>


</section>